    "description": "<br><br>OTXO（读作oh-cho）是一款Rougelike风格的俯视角暴力射击游戏。扮演主角进入一个迷雾重重的豪宅，寻找自己失落的爱。随着你深入这座豪宅，更多的秘密将向你揭开。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/d2e03dccf2076337d799ae56f6216fea.webp?t=1771587345\" width=610 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/dad545ee974f7acbf0d1eb49f758d9ae.poster.avif?t=1771587345\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/dad545ee974f7acbf0d1eb49f758d9ae.webm?t=1771587345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/dad545ee974f7acbf0d1eb49f758d9ae.mp4?t=1771587345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>不知身份，没有名字，更没有自己如何来到这里的记忆…但你记得来到这里的原因。她在这座豪宅的某处等你，而找到她是你唯一的出路。通过各种独特的区域，开辟自己的道路，深入迷团，结交新的盟友，面对自己内心的恶魔，并消灭它们。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/124cf9cc59b7eb13c477c583b757489e.avif?t=1771587345\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/484d248df4c66186b94ca2001a8d64d6.poster.avif?t=1771587345\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/484d248df4c66186b94ca2001a8d64d6.webm?t=1771587345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/484d248df4c66186b94ca2001a8d64d6.mp4?t=1771587345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>借助五花八门的枪支，逾百种技能，破门而入, 并巧用“专注”机制躲避子弹，在弹雨中穿梭自如，清除阻挡你完成任务的各种敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/a439cc94fb52a634a67e2ce7eb531e9a.avif?t=1771587345\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/7e8b7b585ec4ed4fe4f87df917893ad3.poster.avif?t=1771587345\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/7e8b7b585ec4ed4fe4f87df917893ad3.webm?t=1771587345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608640/extras/7e8b7b585ec4ed4fe4f87df917893ad3.mp4?t=1771587345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>◼ <strong>丰富的可再玩性机制</strong>：OTXO将带玩家穿过8个区域，并从超过150间手工打造的房间中随机组合。每局游戏都将带来全新体验。<br>◼ <strong>定制</strong>:从神秘的酒保处获取超过100种的技能，解锁海量武器，找到适合自己的配装以助你打破轮回。<br>◼ <strong>游戏风格</strong>：引入慢动作机制“专注”供你支配，OTXO 会让玩家感到强大的战力和控制力。但是，要小心随着游戏进程出现的各种新敌人，如果不能及时应对的话，他们将轻易逆转局势。<br>◼ <strong>配乐</strong>：通过开发者铿锵有力的原创音乐，带你完全沉浸入优雅而富有节奏的暗黑芭蕾舞剧般的战斗中。",
